1.title: Workout 1 - Posterior Chain, Legs & Metabolic Conditioning

exercises.notes: Standing Calf Raise - 20 Total Reps, First 10 with 2 second pause at top, Second 10 with no pause
Top Half Push-up / Bottom Half Push-up
Military Grip Pull-up - Perform slowly 3 seconds in both directions with 1 second hold at top
Double Dumbbell Biceps Curl - Perform slowly 3 seconds in both directions with 1 second hold at top
Chin Up - Perform slowly 3 seconds in both directions with 1 second hold at top
Alternating Dumbbell Biceps Curl - Perform slowly 3 seconds in both directions with 1 second hold at top
Single Arm Alternating Lateral Shoulder Raise with Top Hold
Standing Alternating Arm Dumbbell Shoulder Press
Dumbbell Shrugs - 15 reps with 2 second hold at top
Alternating Single Arm Dumbbell Chest Fly
Biceps 25 Burner Curl - 5 Alternating Each Arm Low Position, 5 Alternating Each Arm High Position, 5 Full Reps
Dumbbell Plank and Hip Flexor Step Through
Single Single Double Dumbbell Chest Press
Barbell Shrug - 10 Reps every 30 seconds, Repeat 6 times
Rear Delt Raises - 10 Reps every 30 seconds, Repeat 6 times
Iso Chest Contraction-Push-up Flow - 5 Iso Chest Contractions, 5-10 Push-ups, Repeat Flow 3 times consecutively = 1 Round
Alternating Biceps Curl With Top Hold

3.title: Workout 11 - Legs with Emphasis on Quads

exercises.notes: Kettlebell Side Plank Burpee Deadlift Flow - 4 Each side (8 total) Alternating Push-up Side Plank Punch to Deadlift then 5 Deadlifts then 5 Push-ups
Fixed Bent Knee Standing Calf Raises
Standing Alternating Arm Dumbbell Shoulder Press
Single Single Double Incline Dumbbell Chest Press
Dumbbell Pullover with Ascending Close Grip Press - 1 Pullover 1 Close Grip Press, 1 Pullover 2 Close Grip Presses, continue until 8-10 Close Grip Presses
Single Leg Kettlebell RDL with Pendlay Row
Standing Calf Raise - Change speed every 5 alternating between slow reps and fast reps
High Kettlebell Clean to Overhead Press
Single Arm Alternating Lateral Shoulder Raise with Top Hold
Standing Alternating Arm Dumbbell Shoulder Press
Slam Ball Squat to Escalating Overhead Press - Complete as many as possible in 60 Seconds, Increase the number of Overhead Presses by 1 after every slam
Alternating Single Arm Dumbbell Chest Fly
Inside Outside Bench Push-up Flow - 10 Medial/Lateral Plyo Bench Push-ups, 5 Close Grip Bench Push-ups, 10 Medial/Lateral Plyo Bench Push-ups, 5 Close Grip Bench Push-ups
Single Arm Alternating Heavy Band Curl
Single Single Double Incline Dumbbell Chest Press
Reverse Grip Single Arm Cable Triceps Extension
